{"title":"Intoxicacion Baclofeno iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Urgencias/Intoxicacion Baclofeno iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Intoxicación\\Npor Baclofeno","guid":"I5kbboR9RDpnJbf1YKUjfg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Farmacología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Derivado sintético de GABA → agonista selectivo GABA-B","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Usos clínicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"Espasticidad (EM, LME, PC) → indicación FDA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"Trastorno por consumo de alcohol → OFF-LABEL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"Dolor musculoesquelético, ERGE → off-label","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Vías de\\Nadministración","guid":"u_LfH3cbX1OJqdnqek9SDw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"ORAL → biodisponibilidad 70-85%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"INTRATECAL → bomba implantable (casos severos/crónicos)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Farmacocinética","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Peak sérico ~2h post-ingesta oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"t½ normal = 2-6h (promedio 3.5h)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"t½ en SOBREDOSIS = 12-36h (hasta 36h reportado con 450mg)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"Excreción renal ~85% → AJUSTAR en ERC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"Metabolismo hepático minoritario (enzimas CYP no bien definidas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"Vd = 0.7-1 L/kg (moderado)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"10","text":"Unión a proteínas = 30% → DIALIZABLE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"10","text":"Moderadamente lipofílico → redistribución tisular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Puede causar SEGUNDO PEAK tardío por redistribución","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"10","text":"Niveles en LCR ~8.5x menores que plasma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"10","text":"Eliminación del SNC MÁS LENTA que del plasma","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología\\Ny Contexto","guid":"Fqax2Wz_iB_OPVJDnpfpcA","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Incidencia creciente por uso off-label (alcohol)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Dosis terapéutica = 5mg c/8h (máximo 80mg/d)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"Concentración terapéutica = 0.08-0.4 mg/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"Concentración tóxica = 1.1-3.5 mg/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"Concentración coma/fatal = 6.0-9.6 mg/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"22","text":"Toxicidad seria generalmente con >200mg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"22","text":"Dosis >200mg → predictor de delirium, coma, convulsiones, ingreso UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"22","text":"Pacientes con baclofeno >80mg/d → MAYOR riesgo suicida","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Factores de Riesgo\\Nde Toxicidad","guid":"makKiw4R3Em-WvT93Zqhxg","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"INSUFICIENCIA RENAL\\N→ principal factor","guid":"O8XElwZNN9QCiNmx0jRx6g","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Dosis tan bajas como 10mg pueden ser tóxicas en ERC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Acumulación por clearance retardado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"Edad avanzada → farmacocinética alterada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"Dosis altas crónicas (>80mg/d)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"31","text":"Interacciones con otros depresores SNC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"31","text":"Malfunción de\\Nbomba intratecal","guid":"sRJG1Vsaakq8vgZg6vxJaA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Microfuga, desconexión, migración catéter","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"PEORES outcomes que sobredosis oral","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Dosis terapéutica → efecto predominante en MÉDULA ESPINAL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Dosis TÓXICA → pierde selectividad → efecto CEREBRAL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Agonismo\\NGABA-B\\Nexcesivo","guid":"7nKWTO0_X6AKVSbGipr-wg","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"Inhibición presináptica liberación neurotransmisores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"Hiperpolarización neuronal difusa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"Depresión centro respiratorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"Alteración conducción cardíaca","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"41","text":"Mecanismo de convulsiones\\N→ paradójico","guid":"eWdAjNzVWyg0bFlCMRmY9A","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Posible desinhibición cortical por supresión subcortical","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Mecanismo no completamente esclarecido","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"Presentación\\NClínica","guid":"XrWx9YHtVBBkqHezGz7fpg","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Toxicidad\\NLEVE","guid":"IZugWWd7i2ek1Z5gX2KWgw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Somnolencia, letargia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Confusión, cefalea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"Náuseas, mareos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"52","text":"Toxicidad\\NMODERADA","guid":"o7O4c27PNzqNVlVMGbRnWw","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Mioclonías","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Hipotonía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Compromiso de conciencia (GCS 9-13)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"52","text":"Toxicidad\\NSEVERA","guid":"ZFjuGGReFmpILAKo893XPQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"DEPRESIÓN SNC profunda → coma (GCS <9)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Falla respiratoria → VM frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"PUEDE MIMETIZAR\\NMUERTE CEREBRAL","guid":"tN8it4WBPAr_3HPYARvvFQ","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Pérdida de reflejos troncoencefálicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Arreflexia completa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Flacidez generalizada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"REVERSIBLE → no declarar muerte cerebral prematuramente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"61","text":"Convulsiones (~17% en series)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Status epiléptico no convulsivo posible → monitorizar EEG","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"61","text":"Delirium (hipo e hiperactivo)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"52","text":"Manifestaciones\\Ncardiovasculares","guid":"e8Ih-dncCJn_2-c6Cs0woQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Hipotensión y bradicardia → más frecuentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Hipertensión paradójica y taquicardia → reportadas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"QTc prolongado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"Bloqueo AV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"Contracciones auriculares prematuras","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"72","text":"Taquicardia supraventricular","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"52","text":"Manifestaciones\\Nautonómicas","guid":"78Fe0AIeTGNr0drf3rs5qA","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Hipotermia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"Depresión respiratoria central","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"52","text":"Complicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Rabdomiólisis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"Neumonía aspirativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"Lesión renal aguda secundaria","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Clínico\\N→ ALTA\\NSOSPECHA","guid":"6IR5xV1AjVGkXeig6YD72w","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"Historia de uso de baclofeno (oral o bomba IT)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"Hipotonía + flacidez + depresión SNC → tríada sugerente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"Espasticidad e hiperreflexia → pensar en ABSTINENCIA (no toxicidad)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"86","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Niveles plasmáticos de baclofeno\\N(Mayo Clinic FBACS)","guid":"oZH6z7rfaTApg_Y2vWhTfQ","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Turnaround time lento → NO útil para manejo agudo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"NO correlaciona bien con duración del coma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"Eliminación SNC más lenta que sérica → depresión prolongada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"91","text":"Panel toxicológico estándar → NO incluye baclofeno rutinariamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"91","text":"Función renal → CRÍTICO (determina clearance)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"91","text":"Gases arteriales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"91","text":"ELP, glucosa, función hepática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"91","text":"CK (rabdomiólisis)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"86","text":"Estudios\\Ncomplementarios","guid":"8cNVuDy7CeJcsKIDyCH26g","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"EKG → QTc, bloqueos, arritmias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Monitorización cardíaca continua","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"EEG continuo → descartar status no convulsivo en comatosos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"Imagenología → descartar otras causas de coma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"101","text":"Si bomba IT → interrogación del dispositivo + imagen del catéter","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"86","text":"Diagnóstico\\Ndiferencial","guid":"UEh7NctD428yN0yIm3E9lQ","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Intoxicación por opioides → Naloxona sin respuesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"Intoxicación por BZD → Flumazenil sin respuesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"Intoxicación por fenobarbital","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"107","text":"Intoxicación por etanol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"107","text":"ACV → neuroimagen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"107","text":"Encefalopatía metabólica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"107","text":"Status epiléptico no convulsivo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"0","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"SOPORTE → PILAR del tratamiento (no hay antídoto específico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"ABC y\\NEstabilización","guid":"ie_CPf-HIbds0WRcN4a8sQ","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Vía aérea → intubación frecuentemente necesaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Intubación prolongada esperable → iniciar nutrición enteral precoz","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"Ventilación mecánica si falla respiratoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"Soporte hemodinámico → fluidos, vasopresores si necesario","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"115","text":"Descontaminación\\NGI","guid":"QOF_TR1Pv6oUqmdYCloBtw","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"Eficacia NO probada en sobredosis baclofeno","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"Carbón activado → considerar si <1h post-ingesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"Un caso: PEG + carbón activado día 9 con reducción de niveles","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"115","text":"Manejo de\\Nconvulsiones","guid":"raryu_KV9ixD6vlBsFeGOQ","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"BZD primera línea (lorazepam, diazepam)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"Propofol → convulsiones refractarias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"Barbitúricos → segunda línea refractaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"Monitorización EEG continua recomendada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"115","text":"Manejo\\Ncardiovascular","guid":"KeONRbeHhIP2nfzcH7tF6w","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Monitorización continua","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Atropina → bradicardia sintomática","guid":"","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Caso reportado con beneficio en depresión respiratoria/cardíaca","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"Vasopresores si hipotensión refractaria","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"115","text":"Recalentamiento → si hipotermia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"115","text":"Manejo de rabdomiólisis → hidratación agresiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"115","text":"Hemodiálisis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"INDICADA en INSUFICIENCIA RENAL + toxicidad severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"CONTROVERSIAL si\\Nfunción renal normal","guid":"_w_Wce-or_1KFqHotXgCxQ","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"A FAVOR: Vd bajo (0.7L/kg), unión proteica baja (30%), moderadamente lipofílico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"EN CONTRA: en función renal normal, HD no mejora eliminación significativamente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"138","text":"CVVHF → alternativa en inestabilidad hemodinámica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"138","text":"Considerar en intoxicación MASIVA independiente de función renal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"115","text":"Bomba\\Nintratecal","guid":"L_HcWaG2W6Vhpiv7D8P6zQ","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"Consultar INMEDIATAMENTE al especialista de bomba","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"Interrogar dispositivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"Detener bomba por 48h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"145","text":"Considerar drenaje de LCR → más efectivo si PRECOZ","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"145","text":"Remoción tardía de LCR puede ser inefectiva","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"115","text":"ATENCIÓN →\\Nprevenir\\NABSTINENCIA","guid":"uJKJtCRpS3GX3yhUBQTPWw","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"Al resolver toxicidad oral → reiniciar baclofeno a dosis menor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"Bomba IT → reiniciar dentro de 48h de detenida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"151","text":"Abstinencia de baclofeno = EMERGENCIA médica","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"0","text":"Abstinencia por Baclofeno\\N(diagnóstico diferencial)","guid":"-P8f1jaJwtrBWJnkCo8Q1w","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Ocurre por suspensión ABRUPTA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"Clínica OPUESTA a\\Nintoxicación","guid":"Mhr0ZdzQxRIoatUMNf60gw","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Espasticidad, hiperreflexia, rigidez","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Hipertermia → puede ser severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"Agitación, delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"157","text":"Convulsiones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"157","text":"Rabdomiólisis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"157","text":"Inestabilidad autonómica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"157","text":"Falla multiorgánica → puede ser fatal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"155","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"Reinstaurar baclofeno oral → tratamiento definitivo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Resolución completa puede tardar hasta 4 DÍAS (onset oral lento)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"Dexmedetomidina → útil como puente (onset rápido IV)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"No deprime respiración → VENTAJA en AM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"165","text":"BZD IV → complemento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"165","text":"Soporte general (hidratación, manejo hipertermia, rabdomiólisis)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas","guid":"pew3k4P6FoC2PZvKeGNjkA","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"MAYOR riesgo por\\Nfarmacocinética alterada","guid":"J7nbmferT5xwA5JKUOL7qw","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"↓ Clearance renal fisiológico → acumulación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"↑ Sensibilidad SNC a depresores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"↓ Masa muscular → Vd alterado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"172","text":"Polifarmacia → interacciones con otros depresores SNC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"172","text":"Fragilidad → peor tolerancia a complicaciones (VM prolongada, UCI)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"172","text":"Criterios de Beers 2023 → baclofeno NO en lista específica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"PERO considerar riesgo caídas por sedación/hipotonía","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"172","text":"Delirium por intoxicación → puede confundirse con delirium multifactorial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"172","text":"Bomba IT → considerar capacidad cognitiva para reportar síntomas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"172","text":"Deprescripción → considerar alternativas no farmacológicas para espasticidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"172","text":"Recuperación más lenta → anticipar estancia UCI/hospitalaria prolongada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"Mayoría recupera con soporte adecuado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"Mejoría del sensorio esperada en 24-48h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"185","text":"Sobredosis masiva (1-2g) → mayor mortalidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"185","text":"Sobredosis IT → PEORES outcomes que oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"185","text":"Niveles plasmáticos NO predicen bien duración del coma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"185","text":"Reconocimiento e intervención PRECOZ = principal determinante de outcome","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"4BE0-T9oGCsH4TMjcy5U7w","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"PUEDE MIMETIZAR MUERTE CEREBRAL → nunca declarar muerte encefálica sin descartar intoxicación por baclofeno","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"Niveles séricos NO correlacionan con duración del coma → eliminación SNC más lenta que plasmática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"INSUFICIENCIA RENAL = principal factor de riesgo → dosis de 10mg pueden ser tóxicas en ERC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"192","text":"Toxicidad resuelta → REINICIAR baclofeno a dosis menor para PREVENIR abstinencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"192","text":"Dexmedetomidina útil tanto en toxicidad (sedación segura) como en abstinencia (puente al onset oral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"192","text":"Panel toxicológico estándar NO incluye baclofeno → solicitar específicamente si sospecha","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"192","text":"Hemodiálisis controversia → INDICADA claramente solo si ERC + toxicidad severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"192","text":"En AM → siempre considerar delirium por intoxicación en DD de delirium multifactorial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"192","text":"Bomba IT con malfunción → PEORES outcomes → consulta inmediata al especialista","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIÉN","guid":"f7u21EN6t0hd6G7c7UTgEQ","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Síndromes Geriátricos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"→ Sedación UCI (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"→ Deprescripción (Farmacología Geriátrica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"→ Insuficiencia Renal en AM (Nefrología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"→ Muerte Encefálica (Cuidados Intensivos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"→ Criterios de Beers 2023 (Farmacología Geriátrica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Síndromes Geriátricos)","guid":"mC8PMQRKA_UprKO8XkZOyA","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"202","text":"→ Sedación UCI (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"202","text":"→ Criterios de Beers (Farmacología Geriátrica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"1. Dease NM, et al. Baclofen Toxicity. StatPearls. 2023 Mar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"2. Leung NY, et al. Baclofen overdose: defining the spectrum of toxicity. Emerg Med Australas. 2006;18(1):77-82.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"3. Issa A, et al. Baclofen therapeutics, toxicity, and withdrawal: A narrative review. SAGE Open Med. 2021;9:20503121211022197.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"212","text":"4. Labat L, et al. How to Manage Self-Poisoning With Baclofen in AUD? Front Psychiatry. 2018;9:417.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"212","text":"5. Talarico F, et al. Acute Intoxication After Baclofen Administration: A Review. Toxics. 2025;13(11):999.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"212","text":"6. EMCrit: Baclofen — therapy, intoxication, & withdrawal. 2025.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"212","text":"7. Emergency Care BC. Baclofen Toxicity Clinical Summary. 2023.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"212","text":"8. Reichmuth P, et al. Unintentional baclofen intoxication in AUD. BMJ Case Rep. 2015;2015:bcr2015212187.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"212","text":"9. Gautam B, et al. Baclofen overdose: A curious case. Clin Case Rep. 2022;10(8):e6230.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":221,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Urgencias","filename":"Intoxicacion Baclofeno iPad","id":"map_2367","resolved_references":[]}